Quote: Rugby centurion [heading] Salute Mike Hanham, who became Mid-Canterbury's second only rugby centurion when he led his team against North Otago at Oamaru this week. Only other player to represent Mid-Canterbury 100 times was full-back Allan Smith, of Rakaia. Since he branched out on his representative career in 1962, Hanham has made 111 first-class appearances; including one game for the South Island last year ...
